- In [msw_runtime/state/gameplay_runtime.lua](/home/meta_os/MapleWorld/msw_runtime/state/gameplay_runtime.lua#L523), added a bounded `buyFromNpc` request replay cache alongside the existing trade replay cache.
- In [msw_runtime/state/gameplay_runtime.lua](/home/meta_os/MapleWorld/msw_runtime/state/gameplay_runtime.lua#L938), updated `buyFromNpc` to accept a request envelope with `requestId`, short-circuit duplicate envelopes, return the original success payload with `deduped = true`, and emit `npc_buy_applied` / `npc_buy_deduped` replay outcomes.
- In [msw_runtime/state/gameplay_runtime.lua](/home/meta_os/MapleWorld/msw_runtime/state/gameplay_runtime.lua#L971), forwarded `requestId` as the economy `correlationId` so the surviving spend transaction is stable under replay.
- In [tests/economy_runtime_invariant_test.lua](/home/meta_os/MapleWorld/tests/economy_runtime_invariant_test.lua#L107), added one duplicate-submission regression for `buyFromNpc` that selects one affordable NPC item, replays the same request envelope twice, and asserts:
  - exactly one net meso spend
  - exactly one inventory grant
  - exactly one spend transaction
  - one `npc_buy_applied` event and one `npc_buy_deduped` event
  - stable spend `correlationId`

